step unchanged.\n- Candidate list shows no more than 20 items and excludes the edited step.\n\nUnresolved questions:\n\n- Should modal preserve feed scroll/playback state after save?\n\nSource files:\n\n- Task: .agents/tasks/4 - step authoring/4 - implement inline edit modal.md\n- Plan: .agents/tasks/4 - step authoring/4 - implement inline edit modal.plan.md\n- Context: .agents/tasks/4 - step authoring/context.md",
